title: Grateful Dead Live at Poplar Creek Music Theatre on 1983-06-27
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC 24/96; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Wave > Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Promised Land, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Minglewood Blues, Bird Song, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Cold Rain & Snow-> Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Estimated Prophet-> Truckin'-> Drums-> The Other One-> The Wheel-> Good Lovin', E: U.S. Blues
